  "title": "Senior Scientific Support Specialist (Microbiology, up to $2.7K) #HTJ",
  "description": "<p>Office hours, Mon to Fri</p><p>Location: Biopolis (Walkable from Buona Vista)</p><p>Salary: Up to $2,700<br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>● Perform routine and non-routine microbiological testing as part of R&D studies</p><p>● Prepare media, plate samples, incubate, and enumerate colonies</p><p>● Handle and maintain laboratory equipment, ensuring proper calibration and function</p><p>● Maintain lab cleanliness and manage supplies for an organized work environment</p><p>● Follow all site-specific safety and hygiene protocols</p><p>● Communicate any issues or abnormalities to R&D personnel and team leads promptly</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Life Science / Biomedical Science or related</li><li>Some experience / intern in lab would be beneficial</li></ul><p><em>Interested candidates, please forward your resume to</em><em><strong> jalenetan@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></em><br /></p><p><em>Jalene Tan</em><br /><em>Outsourced Team</em><br /><em>Recruit Express Pte Ltd, EA License No.: 99C4599</em></p>",
